        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml ActivityHistorySequenceVi\ntitle 13. Activity History\n\nhide footbox\n\nskinparam shadowing false\nskinparam sequence {\n  ArrowColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBorderColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBackgroundColor #EAF3F7\n  ParticipantBorderColor #2F4858\n  ParticipantBackgroundColor white\n  ParticipantFontColor #1F2D3D\n  ActorBorderColor #2F4858\n  ActorBackgroundColor white\n  ActorFontColor #1F2D3D\n}\n\nautonumber 1\n\nactor \&quot;Admin\&quot; as Admin\nboundary \&quot;ActivityHistory.razor\&quot; as HistoryPage\ncontrol \&quot;AdminApiClient\&quot; as ApiClient\ncontrol \&quot;ActivityLogController\&quot; as ActivityLogController\nentity \&quot;DBContext\&quot; as DBContext\n\nAdmin -&gt; HistoryPage : Mo trang Activity History / nhan Refresh\\n(OnInitializedAsync() / RefreshAsync())\nactivate HistoryPage\n\nHistoryPage -&gt; HistoryPage : Tai du lieu lich su hoat dong\\n(LoadAsync())\n\nHistoryPage -&gt; ApiClient : Gui yeu cau lay lich su hoat dong\\n(GetActivityLogsAsync(query))\nactivate ApiClient\n\nApiClient -&gt; ActivityLogController : Goi API activity log theo bo loc\\n(GET /ActivityLog?page=...&amp;pageSize=...&amp;search=...&amp;action=...&amp;entity=...)\nactivate ActivityLogController\n\nActivityLogController -&gt; DBContext : Xay dung truy van activity logs\\nva loc theo search, action, entity\\n(BuildQuery())\nactivate DBContext\nDBContext --&gt; ActivityLogController : Du lieu activity logs\ndeactivate DBContext\n\nActivityLogController -&gt; ActivityLogController : Sap xep, phan trang va map DTO\n\nActivityLogController --&gt; ApiClient : Tra ve du lieu lich su hoat dong\\n(ActivityLogListDto)\ndeactivate ActivityLogController\n\nApiClient --&gt; HistoryPage : Tra danh sach activity log cho giao dien\ndeactivate ApiClient\n\nHistoryPage -&gt; HistoryPage : Cap nhat Matching Events\\n(_result.TotalCount)\nHistoryPage -&gt; HistoryPage : Cap nhat Actors On Page\\n(DistinctActorCount)\nHistoryPage -&gt; HistoryPage : Cap nhat Current Filters\\n(GetFilterSummary())\nHistoryPage -&gt; HistoryPage : Cap nhat Latest Event\\n(GetLatestLogLabel())\n\nopt Tim kiem va loc activity log\n    Admin -&gt; HistoryPage : Nhap tim kiem / chon action / chon entity\\n(@bind _searchText / @bind _actionFilter / @bind _entityFilter)\n    HistoryPage -&gt; HistoryPage : Dat lai trang va tai lai du lieu\\n(HandleFiltersChangedAsync() / LoadAsync())\nend\n\nopt Phan trang activity log\n    Admin -&gt; HistoryPage : Chuyen trang truoc / sau / chon trang\n    HistoryPage -&gt; HistoryPage : Cap nhat trang hien tai va tai lai du lieu\\n(PreviousPageAsync() / NextPageAsync() / GoToPageAsync() / LoadAsync())\nend\n\nHistoryPage --&gt; Admin : Hien thi Matching Events, Actors On Page,\\nCurrent Filters, Latest Event va bang Activity History\ndeactivate HistoryPage\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="iTsfioeK-e_jtp0syPkg-1">
